[size=3]I DO not OWN any of these mods. this is just a bodyslide preset. if enough people would like, I can add the links for mesh, texture, face, hair and the like later so you may enjoy the mods from previous/ current authors.
This is basically my opinion of a more slender and fitness oriented body. but, be warned, this is an extreme setting and in no way realistic. i do have negative slider sets in bodyslide to set the proportions.
